Body: Description: A substantial amount of deleted files/folders have been deleted but the entries within the database are displayed with NULL values and are not updating properly and doesn't mark the deleted files/folders as deleted.
Invitation updated. Attendees: Scottie Taylor, Steven Schiesl
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed

Steps to Reproduce Updated: Step 1: Use StealthAUDIT for Windows File Systems version 12.0 within the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor platform.  
Step 2: Delete a substantial number of files and folders from the monitored file system.  
Step 3: Check the database entries for the deleted files and folders.  
Step 4: Observe that the database displays NULL values for the entries and does not mark the files and folders as deleted.
